for w in range(1, 6):
    test_config_file = self.test_conf_const.__class__
    data_file, _ = crowdtruth.load(file=TEST_FILE_PREF + 'platform_cf' +
        str(w) + '.csv', config=test_config_file())
    df = pd.read_csv(TEST_FILE_PREF + 'platform_cf' + str(w) + '.csv')
    test_config_df = self.test_conf_const.__class__
    data_df, _ = crowdtruth.load(data_frame=df, config=test_config_df())
    self.assertEqual(set(data_df['units']['duration'].keys()) - set(
        data_file['units']['duration'].keys()), set([]))
    self.assertEqual(set(data_df['workers']['judgment'].keys()) - set(
        data_file['workers']['judgment'].keys()), set([]))
    self.assertEqual(set(data_df['workers']['judgment'] - data_file[
        'workers']['judgment']), set([0]))
